<span id="freeTextContainer5689527810931185927">Parker is a favourite author. I have read all his works (including award winning) and enjoyed them immensely. For some reason or another I decided to read his first trilogy (the only books of his I have not read) and quickly realized I had made a mistake. <br/>Lesson? Don’t be a ‘Backwards Billy’. </span>

          </span>
