        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1984223489" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11417459240395105325">I&apos;m not much of a fan of dark humor, so while I appreciated this for its decent world building and twisted but often appealing characters--and, once they got under way, battles--I don&apos;t feel any need to read the sequels.<br/><br/>Memorable line: &quot;You look as if you died a week ago and they gave you to the apprentice embalmer to practise on.&quot;</span>
  <span id="freeText11417459240395105325" style="display:none">I'm not much of a fan of dark humor, so while I appreciated this for its decent world building and twisted but often appealing characters--and, once they got under way, battles--I don't feel any need to read the sequels.<br /><br />Memorable line: "You look as if you died a week ago and they gave you to the apprentice embalmer to practise on."</span>
