        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1730031942" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14962620490677281040">I was led to believe that this book was super technical, to me it wasn&apos;t really. It does go into some detail about how things work than other books might, but not to a point I would consider overdone. <br/><br/>I expected it to be denser than it actually was. What I got was a fairly fun fantasy novel with some interesting characters that turn out to be pretty damn likable even though I don&apos;t feel like a ton of time was spent building them. <br/><br/>Suspension of disbelief is required from the first page (the syste</span>
  <span id="freeText14962620490677281040" style="display:none">I was led to believe that this book was super technical, to me it wasn't really. It does go into some detail about how things work than other books might, but not to a point I would consider overdone. <br /><br />I expected it to be denser than it actually was. What I got was a fairly fun fantasy novel with some interesting characters that turn out to be pretty damn likable even though I don't feel like a ton of time was spent building them. <br /><br />Suspension of disbelief is required from the first page (the system of law in the primary city revolves around lawyers fighting to the death in most cases) but if you let that go it's worth the read.</span>
  <a data-text-id="14962620490677281040" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

